text: Saint-Germain-de-Tallevende-la-Lande-Vaumont was a commune. It is in the region of Basse-Normandie in the Calvados department. This is in the northwest of France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Vire- Normandie.Arrêté préfectoral 31 December 2015 == References == Category:Former communes in Calvados
title: Saint-Germain-de-Tallevende-la-Lande-Vaumont
